data.description: Wonderful Pflugerville Location Just Blocks from Weiland Elementary School, Stoney Creek Park and Community Amenity Center! Light and Bright Single Story in Desired Gaston-Sheldon Community has 3 Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths. Set on a Landscaped and Tree Shaded Lot this Home Features: Stained Concrete Floors, Updated Ceiling Fans and Lighting and a Neutral Color Palette. Plenty of Room for Family Time in the Spacious Family Room. The Immaculate Eat-In Kitchen features: Stainless Appliances, Gas Range, Breakfast Bar, Walk-In Pantry and an Abundance of Cabinetry and Counter-Space. The Dining Area has a Ceiling Fan and Sliding Door to the Covered Back Patio. The Primary Bedroom has an En-Suite Bath and a Walk-In Closet that has Custom Organizers. There are Two Nicely Sized Secondary Bedrooms, Second Full Bath and Indoor Utility Room. Lots of Room to Play in the Big Back Yard. 8 fruit trees, plus grapevine, asparagus and whisky barrels ready for fall planting. Close to Downtown Pflugerville for Dining, Shops and Events. Minutes to Major Shopping, Roadways and Employers.
